translate russian mari12b_36301338:

    # fr "I'll even cook you dinner."
    fr "Я даже приготовлю тебе ужин."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:183
translate russian mari12b_cfff4e2c:

    # pc "Ha, you don't have to try to convince me. I'd love to spend the day with you."
    pc "Ха, не нужно меня уговаривать. Я с удовольствием проведу день с тобой."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:186
translate russian mari12b_1b4c460c:

    # "I spend the rest of the day hanging out with Mari."
    "Остаток дня я провожу с Мари."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:187
translate russian mari12b_e2f512e0:

    # "I help her out with the chores on her farm, picking vegetables and chatting."
    "Я помогаю ей по хозяйству на ферме, собираю овощи и болтаем."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:190
translate russian mari12b_ddd97615:

    # "We feed the animals and brush her horse, Cash."
    "Мы кормим животных и чистим ее лошадь, Кэша."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:193
translate russian mari12b_4db51a74:

    # "Then we just sit in the fresh air and drink iced tea in the early summer breeze."
    "Потом мы просто сидим на свежем воздухе и пьем холодный чай, наслаждаясь ранним летним ветерком."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:195
translate russian mari12b_d41d8cd9_31:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio36.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio36.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:196
translate russian mari12b_1858b787:

    # fr "This has been great. Spending time with you. Doing things like a couple."
    fr "Это было здорово. Проводить время с тобой. Делать вещи, как пара."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:197
translate russian mari12b_ffc4a85b:

    # pc "Yeah, it's been fun."
    pc "Да, было весело."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:199
translate russian mari12b_d41d8cd9_32:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio37.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio37.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:200
translate russian mari12b_d7d09581:

    # fr "I'd love to do it more often."
    fr "Я бы с удовольствием делала это чаще."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:203
translate russian mari12b_f2e427de:

    # "Then Mari cooks up dinner. It's a mix of different vegetables sauteed together."
    "Потом Мари готовит ужин. Это смесь разных овощей, обжаренных вместе."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:204
translate russian mari12b_169a82ad:

    # "No meat, because she's vegetarian and doesn't have any at the house, but the vegetables are all fresh, and the bread is homemade as well."
    "Без мяса, потому что она вегетарианка и у нее его нет дома, но овощи все свежие, и хлеб тоже домашний."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:205
translate russian mari12b_d574565c:

    # "It's very tasty."
    "Очень вкусно."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:208
translate russian mari12b_756b3b11:

    # "After that, we sit in her living room and watch a movie. The Disney animated Robin Hood - her favorite."
    "После этого мы сидим в ее гостиной и смотрим фильм. Анимационный мультфильм Диснея «Робин Гуд» — ее любимый."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:209
translate russian mari12b_50d1a5c2:

    # "She hums along with all the songs."
    "Она напевает все песни."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:210
translate russian mari12b_bb444f7c:

    # pc "These are definitely going to be in my head for the next week."
    pc "Они точно будут крутиться у меня в голове всю следующую неделю."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:212
translate russian mari12b_d41d8cd9_33:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio37-2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio37-2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:213
translate russian mari12b_8da90cc3:

    # fr "Join the club!"
    fr "Присоединяйся к клубу!"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:216
translate russian mari12b_af7d8e81:

    # "We take a shower together."
    "Мы принимаем душ вместе."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:217
translate russian mari12b_fdf6b91c:

    # "I scrub her back, taking extra time to massage her shoulders."
    "Я мою ей спину, уделяя особое внимание массажу плеч."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:220
translate russian mari12b_5e90d934:

    # "Then we go to bed."
    "Потом мы ложимся спать."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:222
